            <lg xml:id="TK1310">
<l>ūṭa luṇaṅka viṭuvārō ṭeṉṉeñcaṅ </l>
<l>kūṭuvē meṉpa tavā</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is nothing but strong desire that makes her mind unite with me who can leave her to her own dislike.</l>
